OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784620075
OL,3,CMan, 28, charged with murder of Ann
OL,4,CWiddecombe
OL,6,FA 28-year-old man has been charged
OL,7,Fwith the murder of former MP Ann
OL,8,FWiddecombe over a week after he was
OL,9,Ffirst arrested.
OL,11,FJoshua Kerry, from Rotherham, South
OL,12,FYorkshire, is due to appear at
OL,13,FWestminster Magistrates' Court on
OL,14,FTuesday, the Crown Prosecution Service
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,17,FHe was first arrested on suspicion of
OL,18,Fmurder on July 11, two days after the
OL,19,F78-year-old Reform UK spokeswoman was
OL,20,Ffound dead at her home in Devon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784620075
OL,3,CMan, 28, charged with murder of Ann
OL,4,CWiddecombe
OL,6,FOn Monday, police said they were still
OL,7,Fdetermining "his motivations and any
OL,8,Fwider activity he may have been
OL,9,Finvolved in is continuing."
OL,11,FSpeaking outside New Scotland Yard on
OL,12,FMonday, head of UK Counter-Terrorism
OL,13,FPolicing Laurence Taylor said: "Given
OL,14,FAnn Widdecombe's profile and the
OL,15,Ftargeted nature of the attack,
OL,16,Fdetermining the motivation, including
OL,17,Fany possible political motivation,
OL,18,Fremains an active avenue of
OL,19,Finvestigation for our detectives."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784620075
OL,3,CMan, 28, charged with murder of Ann
OL,4,CWiddecombe
OL,6,FHe said that detectives are working
OL,7,Fthrough more than 800 lines of
OL,8,Finquiry, and asked for time for
OL,9,Finvestigators to carry out the work.
OL,11,FTwo days after he was arrested for
OL,12,Fmurder, Kerry was additionally
OL,13,Farrested on suspicion of the
OL,14,Fcommission, preparation or instigation
OL,15,Fof acts of terrorism, but has not been
OL,16,Fcharged with this offence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784620075
OL,3,CMan, 28, charged with murder of Ann
OL,4,CWiddecombe
OL,6,FFrank Ferguson, Chief Crown Prosecutor
OL,7,Fof the CPS Special Crime and Counter
OL,8,FTerrorism Division, said: "We have
OL,9,Fdecided to prosecute Joshua Kerry for
OL,10,Fmurder following a police
OL,11,Finvestigation into the death of Ann
OL,12,FWiddecombe in Haytor, Dartmoor.
OL,14,F"Police inquiries into the defendant's
OL,15,Fmotives are ongoing, including a
OL,16,Fpotential political or terrorist
OL,17,Fconnection.
OL,26,@pD@[OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784620075
OL,3,CMan, 28, charged with murder of Ann
OL,4,CWiddecombe
OL,6,F"Our prosecutors have worked closely
OL,7,Fwith the police to establish that
OL,8,Fthere is sufficient evidence to bring
OL,9,Fthis case to court, and we will
OL,10,Fcontinue working with them as their
OL,11,Finvestigation progresses."
OL,13,FWiddecombe was first elected as a
OL,14,FConservative MP in Kent in 1987, and
OL,15,Fwent on to become an MEP for the
OL,16,FBrexit Party and then a spokeswoman
OL,17,Ffor Reform UK.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
