OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FShe also found fame outside politics
OL,12,Fafter starring in Strictly Come
OL,13,FDancing and Celebrity Big Brother.
OL,15,FTributes were paid to her by figures
OL,16,Facross the political spectrum after
OL,17,Fher death, with Home Secretary Shabana
OL,18,FMahmood calling her "one of those rare
OL,19,Fpoliticians who was bigger than
OL,20,Fpolitics".
OL,26,@zD@UOU|D@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/8
