FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1784620075
OL,3,CMan, 28, charged with murder of Ann
OL,4,CWiddecombe
OL,6,FPrime Minister Andy Burnham called for
OL,7,Fa serious review of MPs' safety after
OL,8,Fshe died, and Taylor said officers are
OL,9,Fworking with parliamentary officials
OL,10,Fto make politicians aware of
OL,11,Fprotection measures that are in place.
OL,13,FHe said: "I know many have been
OL,14,Funderstandably concerned about their
OL,15,Fown safety after this horrendous
OL,16,Fattack, particularly after hearing
OL,17,Fabout the nature of the attack she
OL,18,Fendured in her own home.
OL,26,@uD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
